        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3391102850" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5123513004890378327">This is the first book in the Stillhouse Lake series. I was really looking forward to this series however I did not like it as much as I thought I would. <br/>I would have liked detailed descriptions of small town life in America and more in depth characterisation. <br/>I thought the story was obviously implausible at times, but when I suspended my disbelief and sunk into the read I did enjoy it. I will read the next in the series but if I feel the same about the second one, I will stop there.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

